,"channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#ai-ops","cachedResultName":"#ai-ops"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[5562,1420],"id":"37209fdb-1f51-432c-af6a-3e36fc90ccaf","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Daily Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — daily at 7:00. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Pull Side A (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"d2291b5b-b88a-9652-a38f-4f0ebd09566b","name":"Note: Daily Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Pull Side A (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,250],"id":"74e1b59c-c733-61fc-6512-e09274e097dd","name":"Note: Pull Side A (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Pull Side B (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,790],"id":"c7b1d28d-0b25-844e-3ca8-4c331d26917b","name":"Note: Pull Side B (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Diff the Two Systems\n\nDiffs two streams by key into 4 lanes: only-in-A, same, different, only-in-B — the heart of the sync.\n\nPorts: ①→ Create Missing in Google Sheets · ②→ Count In-Sync Rows · ③→ Apply Updates to Google Sheets · ④→ Backfill into HubSpot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"7418f3b6-fc76-8672-6a18-0d21ae18ceef","name":"Note: Diff the Two Systems"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Create Missing in Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,-80],"id":"5d10ab80-a9d3-4add-86ec-f70ada52eb21","name":"Note: Create Missing in Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Count In-Sync Rows\n\nCollapses all items into a single summary item (for counts and run stats).\n\nNext: Gather Sync Results","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,340],"id":"d8856a36-424e-cd1c-1c7e-810630471c58","name":"Note: Count In-Sync Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Apply Updates to Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,760],"id":"3f72c484-2322-0d6b-03f0-7d954234229e","name":"Note: Apply Updates to Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Backfill into HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,1180],"id":"3406cbba-d5d9-05ea-0b28-ce371e55f273","name":"Note: Backfill into HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Gather Sync Results\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"aa9bd455-9d2e-6f13-32dc-c565fd75aa6e","name":"Note: Gather Sync Results"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 50 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"13806fef-d700-4675-cf55-1d20643b9ef9","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"37b7ec38-5b4e-6741-ad57-f118ec1d8e37","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"f6732088-b12e-27b4-3060-9d8813b14c79","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"ba34be6d-0a3c-e696-2ccc-b1944caa2a41","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"74cf53fa-de17-3fad-d09a-bbab21578136","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,1540],"id":"578f1a09-ea04-62cf-6a1e-ae2adb54ca54","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,1540],"id":"d770f0ea-2800-5ec4-86eb-3fecd3c0e3cc","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Clean contact records with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API with instant alerts for Task Automation\n\n**Pattern:** Data Enrichment · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nClean contact records with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API with instant alerts for Task Automation. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual task automation is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Pull Side A (HubSpot) → Diff the Two Systems → Create Missing in Google Sheets → Gather Sync Results → Cap Batch Volume → Stamp Processing Time → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to data enrichment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating task automation in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Responds in seconds\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"1349b1e3-61e4-9940-9e86-9baced4e8a97","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-620],"id":"2fbce907-efab-36ea-bb51-057975c180be","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-620],"id":"e9226da7-2a3c-a548-2849-592d872f9dab","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your task automation process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-620],"id":"6b15ced8-a92f-66eb-08bc-0a42fed3ed9c","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Pull Side A (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Pull Side B (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Pull Side A (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff the Two Systems","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Pull Side B (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff the Two Systems","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Diff the Two Systems":{"main":[[{"node":"Create Missing in Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Count In-Sync Rows","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Apply Updates to Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Backfill into HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Create Missing in Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Count In-Sync Rows":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Apply Updates to Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Backfill into HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Gather Sync Results","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Gather Sync Results":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"317651e2-92a6-48e3-9e73-2a9ef4206262","id":"FDX01737"}